> *A recursive, reflective POETRY algorithm variant using Goedel-Prover-V2*

**GÃ¶del's Poetry** is an advanced automated theorem proving system that combines Large Language Models (LLMs) with formal verification in Lean 4. The system takes mathematical theoremsâ€”either in informal natural language or formal Lean syntaxâ€”and automatically generates verified proofs through a sophisticated multi-agent architecture.

- **Github repository**: <https://github.com/KellyJDavis/goedels-poetry/>
- **Documentation**: <https://KellyJDavis.github.io/goedels-poetry/>

